name: Corporal Grenwick
Lore: 'Death Star trooper who witnessed Leia''s interrogation. Senior tactical advisor to Sergeant Major Enfield. Coordinates security duty assignments for Detention Block AA-23.',
Text: 'While Grenwick is on Death Star, your Death Star Sentry is not unique ( •), is doubled, deploys free, applies all three of its modifiers and is immune to Alter. Power -1 when not on Death Star.',
